//Siege class def file.

ClassInfo
{
	name				"Tat_RJedi"
	weapons				WP_SABER|WP_MELEE|WP_BLASTER_PISTOL
	attributes			MB_ATT_FP_SABER_DEFENSE,1|MB_ATT_GUN_DEFENSE,1|MB_ATT_DEFLECT,2|MB_ATT_PISTOL,3
	saber1				single_3
	sabercolor			4
	saberstyle			SS_MEDIUM|SS_FAST|SS_STRONG
	forcepowers			FP_PUSH,3|FP_PULL,2|FP_SPEED,3|FP_TELEPATHY,2|FP_SABER_OFFENSE,3|FP_SABER_DEFENSE,1|FP_LEVITATION,2
	forcepool			125
	maxhealth			100
	maxarmor			0
	speed				1.03
	modelscale			0.97
	model				"jedi_tf" 				//this is optional, if it's here it forces the model to this.
	skin				"default"					//this is optional, if it's here it forces the skin to this.
	uishader			"models/players/jedi_tf/mb2_icon_default"
	MBClass				MB_CLASS_JEDI
	classNumberLimit	1
}

description	"Jedi Padawan Zia Sram

^2Weaponry:
- Lightsaber
-- Yellow / Red / Blue Styles
-- Saber / Blaster Defense (1)
-- Blaster Deflect (2)
- Blaster Pistol (3)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump  (2)
- Push  (3)
- Pull  (2)
- Speed (3)
- Mind Trick (2)

One of the survivors of the Jedi Purge, this Jedi Padawan found aid and refuge amongst a group of rebel sympathizers on Tatooine, who she promised to help in return. However, word spread quickly among the locals about a trickster using some sort of mental magic to dupe local arms dealers out of their merchandise. This quickly drew the attention of stationed Imperial forces who were unwilling to take the chance of leaving this rumor uninvestigated."